  "text": "Rescue experiments were performed as described before [CITATION_1] . Total RNA was isolated from 50-50 uninjected and b-catenin-2 mRNA injected embryos with TRIZOL (Invitrogen), using the manufacturer's protocol. An extra round of ethanol precipitation was applied in order to eliminate residual TRIZOL contaminations.",
